title: Jon Stewart's 'Daily Show' return is so smooth, it's like he never left
description: Stewart eased back into the host's chair Monday night without missing a beat, firing off jokes with a familiar style that felt like he had left just a few weeks ago, rather than in 2015.

title: Border security dominates in New York special election to replace Rep. Santos
description: Border politics have dominated the special election to replace expelled former Rep. George Santos in a critical swing district in New York.

title: The 2024 Super Bowl becomes the most watched NFL championship in history
description: About 123 million people tuned in across platforms, including CBS, Paramount+, Univision and Nickelodeon. The Kansas City Chiefs defeated the San Francisco 49ers in a game that went to overtime.
